# Normalize line endings across platforms (this is a cross-platform project, §2.12).
# Text files are stored as LF in the repo; Git converts on checkout per OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly binary — never touch these.
# .doc here is Confluence MHTML: it is MIME-structured (CRLF-significant), so
# never let Git normalize its line endings.
*.doc binary
*.docx binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.onnx binary
